docs.snippet: RIO DE JANEIRO, Aug. 18. -The giant airliner Brazilian Clipper arrived at Para today at 5 P.M., alighting at the Rio Guaruja Pan American Airways airport before a huge crowd massed along the avenue facing the airdrome. The throng cheered the North...
docs.lead_paragraph: RIO DE JANEIRO, Aug. 18. -The giant airliner Brazilian Clipper arrived at Para today at 5 P.M., alighting at the Rio Guaruja Pan American Airways airport before a huge crowd massed along the avenue facing the airdrome. The throng cheered the North American newspaper executives aboard the plane.
docs.abstract: at Para, Brazil; welcomed by govt officials

headline.main: BRAZILIAN CLIPPER ARRIVES IN BRAZIL; American Newspaper Heads on Giant Air Liner Receive Warm Welcome at Para.

docs.lead_paragraph: Measured by the quotation for the French franc, the dollar sold to a low of 99.04 cents of its new parity, when the franc on Monday was quoted at 6.69 3/4. The high for the week was 99.73 cents and it closed at 99.44 cents, a net gain of 0.36 cent. Range a year ago was 75.41 high, 72.62 low, 73.40 final price.
